  "detailed_description": "You've found \"100 Pumpkins,\" now find 100 more! The second in the 100 Pumpkins series.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.mp4?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>More pumpkins! More challenge! More puzzles! More bosses! More pitchforks! ...Did I mention more pumpkins?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=270 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.mp4?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In an interconnected world, you'll have to find exactly 1 pumpkin per screen to finish the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/56fd509022889b745c155e7581e571c8.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=270 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/56fd509022889b745c155e7581e571c8.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/56fd509022889b745c155e7581e571c8.mp4?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Key features:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Compact layout<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Minimap and full map showing location and completion<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Checkpoints on each screen<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Return pumpkins home for item rewards like double jump<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>New pitchfork platform mechanic<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Endings based on number of lives lost/time completed<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Upgraded bosses<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Now with music!<br><br>Requests from previous games realized:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/96d4e2ce16a0ab04a3154022a4204808.webp?t=1753466863\" width=16 height=16 /></span>Remap controls option, warping, retry faster after falling, more dynamic layouts",
  "about_the_game": "You've found \"100 Pumpkins,\" now find 100 more! The second in the 100 Pumpkins series.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/fd94d42fd2dc0f724e899a5c8b91ad2f.mp4?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>More pumpkins! More challenge! More puzzles! More bosses! More pitchforks! ...Did I mention more pumpkins?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=270 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/0f37e523a96c488073853ca527cf9477.mp4?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In an interconnected world, you'll have to find exactly 1 pumpkin per screen to finish the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/56fd509022889b745c155e7581e571c8.poster.avif?t=1753466863\" width=270 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824290/extras/56fd509022889b745c155e7581e571c8.webm?t=1753466863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=